COMMERCIAL INSURANCE COMPANY v. James E. REDFORD et al. No. 7213. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Feb. 13, 1963. Colmery & Russell, Topeka, Kan., for appellant. Robert L. Deam, Junction City, Kan., for appellees.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed February 13, 1963, on motion of appellant.
